## Wireframe Style

- **Black and white only** - No colors, grayscale for emphasis
- **Placeholder content** - Lorem ipsum, placeholder images
- **Lucide icons** - Consistent icon library
- **Annotations** - Numbered callouts explaining interactions

## Device Types

### Mobile (375px viewport)
- Single column layouts
- Touch-friendly targets (44px min)
- Bottom navigation patterns
- Swipe gestures noted

### Tablet (768px viewport)
- Adaptive layouts
- Split views where appropriate
- Landscape considerations

### Desktop (1024px+ viewport)
- Multi-column layouts
- Sidebar navigation
- Hover states noted

## Key Components

- **Device frames** - Phone/tablet/desktop outlines
- **Navigation patterns** - Tab bars, hamburger menus, sidebars
- **Form elements** - Inputs, buttons, checkboxes
- **Cards & lists** - Content containers
- **Modals & overlays** - Dialog patterns
- **Annotation markers** - Numbered circles with explanations

## Annotation Format

```
① Navigation - Sticky top bar with logo and menu
② Search - Expandable search with autocomplete
③ Content - Scrollable feed with infinite scroll
④ Action - Floating action button for new post
```

